D2EDF1;\" colspan=\"2\" |'''29'''\n| colspan=\"3\" |\u2013\n| colspan=\"1\" |10\n| colspan=\"2\" |20\n|-\n| [https://www.unique-research.at/aktuelle-umfragen/profil-umfrage-koalitionspr\u00e4ferenzen-nach-der-wahl Unique Research]\n| data-sort-value=\"2019-10-03\"| 30 Sep\u20133 Oct 2019\n| 500\n| Online\n| style=\"background:#D2EDF1;\" colspan=\"2\" |'''23'''\n| colspan=\"2\" |12\n| colspan=\"2\" |21\n| colspan=\"3\" |18\n| colspan=\"1\" |9\n| colspan=\"2\" |17\n|}\n\n== Hypothetical polling ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:90%;line-height:14px;\"\n|- style=\"height:40px;\"\n! style=\"width:200px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Polling firm\n! style=\"width:120px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Fieldwork date\n! style=\"width:80px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sample<br>size\n! style=\"width:35px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Method\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[Austrian People's Party|\u00d6VP]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[Social Democratic Party of Austria|SP\u00d6]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[Freedom Party of Austria|FP\u00d6]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[The Greens \u2013 The Green Alternative|Gr\u00fcne]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[NEOS \u2013 The New Austria and Liberal Forum|NEOS]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| [[Peter Pilz List|JETZT]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| List [[Heinz-Christian Strache|Strache]]/[[The Alliance for Austria|DA\u00d6]]\n! class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\"| Others\n! rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\" style=\"width:60px;\" | Lead\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Austrian People's Party (2017)/meta/color}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Social Democratic Party of Austria/meta/color}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Freedom Party of Austria/meta/color}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{The Greens \u2013 The Green Alternative/meta/color}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{NEOS \u2013 The New Austria and Liberal Forum/meta/color