stock.com/blog/country-chart-news-the-top-30-digital-singles-april-2-2014-florida-georgia-line-1-jerrod-niemann-dierks-bentley-gold-luke-bryan-leads-6-near-gold-singles-stars|title=Country Chart News - The Top 30 Digital Singles - April 2, 2014: Florida Georgia Line #1, Jerrod Niemann & Dierks Bentley Gold, Luke Bryan Leads 6 Near-Gold Singles & Stars {{!}} New Country Music, Listen to Songs & Video {{!}} Roughstock.com|date=2014-04-07|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref>\n| \n* RIAA: 3\u00d7 Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=United States|type=single|title=It Goes Like This|artist=Thomas Rhett}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Get Me Some of That]]\"\n| 4\n| 1\n| 41\n| \u2014\n| 6\n| 49\n|\n* US: 747,000<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152826/http://www.roughstock.com/blog/country-chart-news-the-top-30-digital-singles-for-june-19-2014|title=Country Chart News: The Top 30 Digital Singles For June 19, 2014 {{!}} New Country Music, Listen to Songs & Video {{!}} Roughstock.com|date=2014-07-14|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref>\n|\n* RIAA: 2\u00d7 Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=United States|type=single|title=Get Me Some of That|artist=Thomas Rhett}}\n|-\n| 2014\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Make Me Wanna]]\"\n| 2\n| 1\n| 43\n| \u2014\n| 11\n| 74\n|\n* US: 596,000<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://roughstock.com/news/2015/04/34661-country-musics-top-30-digital-singles-week-of-april-29-2015/|title=Country Music's Top 30 Digital Singles: Week of April 29, 2015 {{!}} RoughStock|work=RoughStock|access-date=2018-01-04}}</ref>\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=United States|type=single|title=Make Me Wanna|artist=Thomas Rhett}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2015\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Crash and Burn (Thomas Rhett song)|Crash and Burn]]\"\n| 2\n| 1\n| 36\n| \u2014\n| 1\n| 47\n|\n* US: 882,000<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://roughstock.com/news/2016/01/39625-top-30-digital-country-singles-chart-january-19-2016|title=Top 30 Digital Country Singles Chart: January 19, 20